Abstrak:
One of the aliens was still alive. We had watched the fire streaking down
from the sky and the egg smash\ down. As soon as the egg cooled down a bit,
we had gathered on the site to find out what it was. Our party was about to enter the broken egg when we saw movement, and prudently waited for the aliens
to emerge from the egg. Or to offer help if they couldn’t.
Fakultas: Fakultas Matematika dan Ilmu Pengetahuan Alam
